@startuml svc-weather--get-weather-alerts

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2563eb
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-weather/#integration-context ⬆ svc-weather Integration Context]]

title GET /weather/alerts\nGet active weather alerts for a region

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-weather" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-weather/]] #F1F5F9
participant "OpenWeather API" as ExtWx [[/actors/#openweather-api]] #F3F4F6
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "Valkey + PG" as DB [[/microservices/svc-weather/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-weather.html#/Alerts/getWeatherAlerts View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : GET /weather/alerts
activate GW #2563eb
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #2563eb

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> ExtWx : Fetch active alerts
activate ExtWx #F3F4F6
ExtWx --> Svc : OK
deactivate ExtWx

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT ... WHERE filters
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Page of results
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Distribute severe weather alerts]]

Svc --> GW : 200 OK
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 200 OK
deactivate GW

@enduml